{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they would go out into the fields on a picnic or something, and he showed them-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] Oh, I'm so sorry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Show them how to get across the mountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it worked, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A lot of people went over that way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a lot of other ideas that didn't work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like for example, we were going to take a boat and just go around like that and come back on Portbou, get to Portbou, but never did materialize.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So many of our plans never materialized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And obviously, some people were caught, but there was a Major [INAUDIBLE], a British military attache in Spain, and quite a few people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Bone ?] and a few people who in Spain, if they were caught, they would find ways to get them out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Two or three people-- not two or three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe a dozen or more over the year were caught in Spain without the proper papers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Here's what you had to have.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You had to have-- before the Portuguese would let you in-- we think there were a lot of collaborators in Portugal, a lot of them-- before they would let you in, you had to have a visa saying that you were going somewhere else because too many people were there, were over populating.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You couldn't get a hotel anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember the Chinese visa said, under no circumstances is the bearer of this-- this visa allowed into China.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But it served the purpose because nobody read Chinese, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But you had to have that visa and a passage on the ship or on-- on the clipper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The clipper was just operating in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, oh, there were-- a lot of bribing went on.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
